<section class="suds-services">
  <div class="suds-services__wrap">
    <p class="suds-services__eyebrow">Choose the right mobile detail</p>
    <h1>Premium mobile detailing packages built around vehicle condition.</h1>
    <p class="suds-services__lead">
      Book the package that matches your vehicle, or share the year, make, model, city, and photos if you want a recommendation.
      Suds Auto Salon comes to you for interior and exterior mobile detailing, protection work, and maintenance service around Seattle.
    </p>

    <div class="suds-services__grid">
      <article>
        <h2>Basic Detail</h2>
        <p class="suds-services__price">Clean upkeep for maintained vehicles</p>
        <p>For vehicles that already stay fairly clean and need a lighter interior and exterior refresh.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Light interior refresh</li>
          <li>Hand wash and dry</li>
          <li>Interior and exterior glass</li>
          <li>Best between deeper details</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="suds-services__card-link" href="/pages/basic-detail">View Basic Detail</a>
      </article>

      <article class="suds-services__featured">
        <h2>Signature Detail</h2>
        <p class="suds-services__price">Best first booking</p>
        <p>The best choice for most drivers who want a proper inside-and-out reset in one mobile appointment.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Interior reset</li>
          <li>Careful exterior hand wash</li>
          <li>Wheels, tires, glass, and finish care</li>
          <li>Protection add-ons available</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="suds-services__card-link" href="/pages/signature-detail">View Signature Detail</a>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h2>Elite Detail</h2>
        <p class="suds-services__price">Premium deep reset</p>
        <p>For heavier buildup, resale prep, pet vehicles, family SUVs, rough exterior feel, and vehicles that need more time.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Deeper interior reset</li>
          <li>Clay bar exterior treatment</li>
          <li>Premium hand wax</li>
          <li>Strongest non-coating detail</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="suds-services__card-link" href="/pages/elite-detail">View Elite Detail</a>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h2>Ceramic Coating</h2>
        <p class="suds-services__price">Gloss and protection</p>
        <p>For drivers who want stronger paint protection, easier washing, better gloss, and longer-lasting protection than wax.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Paint prep and decontamination</li>
          <li>Ceramic coating application</li>
          <li>Gloss and slickness</li>
          <li>Care guidance after service</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="suds-services__card-link" href="/pages/ceramic-coating">View Ceramic Coating</a>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h2>Maintenance Plan</h2>
        <p class="suds-services__price">Recurring clean vehicle care</p>
        <p>After the first reset, monthly maintenance keeps the car clean without letting buildup take over again.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Priority scheduling</li>
          <li>Monthly or recurring service</li>
          <li>Ideal after Signature or Elite Detail</li>
          <li>Monthly service options available</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="suds-services__card-link" href="/pages/maintenance-detailing">View Maintenance Plans</a>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h2>Add-Ons</h2>
        <p class="suds-services__price">Priced by condition</p>
        <p>Add targeted services when the vehicle needs more than a standard package.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Pet hair removal</li>
          <li>Stain extraction</li>
          <li>Odor treatment</li>
          <li>Trim, glass, wheel, and paint protection</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="suds-services__card-link" href="/pages/services">Compare Services</a>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="suds-services__cta">
      <div>
        <h2>Not sure what to book?</h2>
        <p>Send the vehicle details and Suds will recommend the right package before you book.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/pages/contact-us">Request a Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .suds-services {
    background: #090909;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .suds-services__wrap {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 58px 20px;
  }

  .suds-services__eyebrow,
  .suds-services__price {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #f2d36b;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .suds-services h1 {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(3.4rem, 6vw, 6.4rem);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .suds-services h2 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .suds-services__lead {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 20px 0 0;
    color: #e8e8e8;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .suds-services__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .suds-services article,
  .suds-services__cta {
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .16);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px;
    background: #121212;
  }

  .suds-services__featured {
    border-color: #f2d36b;
    background: #1b170d;
  }

  .suds-services article p,
  .suds-services li,
  .suds-services__cta p {
    color: #e8e8e8;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .suds-services ul {
    margin: 16px 0 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .suds-services__card-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    margin-top: 18px;
    color: #f2d36b;
    font-weight: 900;
    text-underline-offset: 4px;
  }

  .suds-services__cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .suds-services__cta div {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .suds-services__cta a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 48px;
    padding: 13px 20px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: #f2d36b;
    color: #090909;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 900px) {
    .suds-services__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .suds-services__wrap {
      padding: 44px 18px;
    }

    .suds-services__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .suds-services__cta {
      align-items: stretch;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .suds-services__cta a {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>

